  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3217bd4f8daa9064d98c493af6d679ac, type: 3}
  description: "\u0110\u1ED3ng Th\xE1p l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng
    \u0110\u1ED3ng b\u1EB1ng s\xF4ng C\u1EEDu Long \u1EDF ph\xEDa Nam c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t
    Nam, gi\xE1p bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi v\u1EDBi Campuchia. T\u1EC9nh n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng
    v\u1EDBi c\u1EA3nh quan s\xF4ng n\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng v\xE0
    nh\u1EEFng c\xE1nh \u0111\u1ED3ng sen r\u1ED9ng l\u1EDBn, v\xEC v\u1EADy \u0110\u1ED3ng
    Th\xE1p c\xF2n \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c g\u1ECDi l\xE0 \u201C\u0111\u1EA5t sen h\u1ED3ng\u201D.
    M\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC3m du l\u1ECBch n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt c\u1EE7a
    t\u1EC9nh l\xE0 V\u01B0\u1EDDn qu\u1ED1c gia Tr\xE0m Chim, n\u01A1i c\xF3 h\u1EC7
    sinh th\xE1i \u0111\u1EA5t ng\u1EADp n\u01B0\u1EDBc phong ph\xFA v\xE0 l\xE0
    n\u01A1i sinh s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a nhi\u1EC1u lo\xE0i chim qu\xFD hi\u1EBFm. Ngo\xE0i
    ra, \u0110\u1ED3ng Th\xE1p c\xF2n c\xF3 n\u1EC1n n\xF4ng nghi\u1EC7p ph\xE1t
    tri\u1EC3n m\u1EA1nh v\u1EDBi c\xE1c s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m nh\u01B0 l\xFAa g\u1EA1o,
    tr\xE1i c\xE2y v\xE0 th\u1EE7y s\u1EA3n."
  desSatNhap: "C\u0103n c\u1EE9 theo n\u1ED9i dung Ngh\u1ECB quy\u1EBFt s\u1ED1 202/2025/QH15,
    to\xE0n b\u1ED9 di\u1EC7n t\xEDch t\u1EF1 nhi\xEAn v\xE0 quy m\xF4 d\xE2n s\u1ED1
    c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh Ti\u1EC1n Giang v\xE0 t\u1EC9nh \u0110\u1ED3ng Th\xE1p \u0111\xE3
    \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c s\xE1p nh\u1EADp ho\xE0n to\xE0n. \u0110\u01A1n v\u1ECB h\xE0nh
    ch\xEDnh h\u1EE3p nh\u1EA5t sau s\xE1p nh\u1EADp ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c mang t\xEAn
    g\u1ECDi l\xE0 t\u1EC9nh \u0110\u1ED3ng Th\xE1p."
